OL,7,FA Cambridge graduate who died after
OL,8,Frefusing chemotherapy was "adversely
OL,9,Finfluenced" by her conspiracy theorist
OL,10,Fmother whose actions were
OL,11,F"incomprehensible", a coroner has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FPaloma Shemirani, 23, collapsed on
OL,15,FJuly 19 last year and was taken to
OL,16,FRoyal Sussex County Hospital where she
OL,17,Fdied five days later.
