OL,8,Fnon-Hodgkin lymphoma and instead
OL,9,Ffollowed an "alternative" treatment
OL,10,Fplan including daily coffee enemas
OL,11,Fadvised by her parents.
OL,13,FAn osteopath who saw Miss Shemirani on
OL,14,Fthe morning she collapsed said he had
OL,15,F"never seen" a lymphoid mass like hers
