OL,7,FHer mother, Kay "Kate" Shemirani, a
OL,8,Fprominent online conspiracy theorist,
OL,9,Fand her father, Dr Faramarz Shemirani,
OL,10,Fwho is "sympathetic" to his ex-wife's
OL,11,Fviews, tried to blame medical staff
OL,12,Ffor their daughter's death.
OL,14,FToday (2 October) at Kent and Medway
OL,15,FCoroner's Court in Maidstone, coroner
OL,16,FCatherine Wood concluded that their
OL,17,Finfluence on Miss Shemirani "more than
OL,18,Fminimally" contributed to her death.
