OL,7,FMs Wood said: "In December 2023,
OL,8,FPaloma Shemirani attended the
OL,9,FMaidstone Hospital and was found to
OL,10,Fhave a large and bulky upper right
OL,11,Fside medicinal mass...There is no
OL,12,Fdoubt that the mass was a non-Hodgkin
OL,13,Flymphoma."
OL,15,FHer mother questioned medical staff to
OL,16,Fthe extent that the coroner found it
OL,17,F"highly likely that she seeded some
OL,18,Fform of doubt in Paloma's mind as to
OL,19,Fher diagnosis".
