OL,7,FMs Shemirani was struck off as a nurse
OL,8,Fin 2021, and a Nursing and Midwifery
OL,9,FCouncil committee found she had spread
OL,10,FCovid-19 misinformation that "put the
OL,11,Fpublic at a significant risk of harm".
OL,13,F"Mrs Shemirani took a leading role in
OL,14,Fadvising Paloma in respect of and
OL,15,Ffacilitating access to alternative
OL,16,Ftreatments," said Ms Wood.
