OL,7,FAfter graduating from Cambridge, Miss
OL,8,FShemirani was working and living in a
OL,9,Fflat with a housemate and was
OL,10,F"estranged" from her mother until her
OL,11,Fcancer diagnosis.
OL,13,FMs Shemirani encouraged her to come
OL,14,Fback to the family home and took a
OL,15,Fleading role in Miss Shemirani's
OL,16,Falternative "treatment programme",
OL,17,Fwhich involved daily coffee enemas and
OL,18,Fa strict diet, the inquest heard.
