OL,7,FAt the time of her diagnosis, doctors
OL,8,Fat Maidstone Hospital told Miss
OL,9,FShemirani she had an 80% chance of
OL,10,Frecovery through chemotherapy.
OL,12,FThe coroner said: "It seems that if
OL,13,FPaloma had been supported and
OL,14,Fencouraged to accept her diagnosis and
OL,15,Fconsidered chemotherapy with an open
OL,16,Fmind she probably would have followed
OL,17,Fthat course."
