OL,7,FAn osteopath who saw her that day,
OL,8,FNick Gosset, said he could feel large
OL,9,Flumps in her shoulder that went all
OL,10,Fthe way up into her neck, but that she
OL,11,Fhad refused any suggestion of a
OL,12,Freferral to conventional treatment.
OL,14,F"I felt I was presented with a young
OL,15,Fwoman ` and I'm not an expert in this,
OL,16,Fmy field is biomechanics ` a young
OL,17,Flady who was in the last stages of a
OL,18,Fvery difficult disease, and she had
OL,19,Fdeclined to engage with conventional
OL,20,Ftreatment," he said.
