OL,7,FMiss Shemirani's twin brother Gabriel
OL,8,FShemirani told the inquest "I blame my
OL,9,Fmother entirely for my sister's
OL,10,Fdeath", by "obstructing" his sister
OL,11,Ffrom receiving treatment.
OL,13,FMr Shemirani alleged that he and his
OL,14,Fsiblings "felt unsafe" around their
OL,15,Fmother and that she had been
OL,16,F"emotionally distant" and physically
OL,17,Fabusive to them as children.
OL,19,FHe further alleged during his evidence
OL,20,Fthat his father was also physically
OL,21,Fabusive to him and his brother.
