OL,7,FOutside the court, Mr Shemirani said
OL,8,Fthe state had "failed" by not classing
OL,9,Fhis sister's death as an unlawful
OL,10,Fkilling, despite recognising a breach
OL,11,Fin their duty of care.
OL,13,FIt was noted in Miss Shemirani's
OL,14,Finitial hospital admittance in autumn
OL,15,F2023 that she had "recently moved out
OL,16,Fof her mother's house due to emotional
OL,17,Fand physical abuse including food
OL,18,Frestrictions" by doctors at Maidstone
OL,19,FHospital.
