OL,8,Fduring her stay at Maidstone Hospital
OL,9,Fin December 2023 showed them advising
OL,10,Fher insistently to "discharge herself".
OL,12,FHer father sent her messages saying
OL,13,F"you must discharge yourself" and "you
OL,14,Fwill politely say you want to go home
OL,15,Fnow" once he had heard about her
OL,16,Fdiagnosis.
