OL,7,FMs Shemirani also sent Miss
OL,8,FShemirani's then boyfriend a voice
OL,9,Fnote telling him to bring her to their
OL,10,Ffamily home and saying "she's really
OL,11,Fnot going to be going in or out of
OL,12,Fanywhere", while she looked after her.
OL,14,F"Mrs Shemirani was asked whether this
OL,15,Fmeant she was taking steps to manage
OL,16,Fand control Paloma's treatment but she
OL,17,Fdid not accept this," said Ms Wood.
