OL,7,FIn April 2024, Miss Shemirani's twin
OL,8,Fbrother brought a High Court case to
OL,9,Fassess his sister's ability to
OL,10,Fexercise her capacity to make medical
OL,11,Fdecisions.
OL,13,FThe case made slow progress, and while
OL,14,FMiss Shemirani gave a witness
OL,15,Fstatement saying she was making her
OL,16,Fown choices, she had said in a text
OL,17,Fthat she was being "kept out" of the
OL,18,Fproceedings, the court heard.
OL,26,@yD@TOUyD@]O]
