OL,5,Cmother
OL,7,FThe coroner noted the "striking"
OL,8,Ffamily dysfunction which had been "on
OL,9,Fdisplay very publicly" during the
OL,10,Finquest.
OL,12,F"The dynamics within the immediate
OL,13,Ffamily were complicated and
OL,14,Fdysfunctional at the time of Paloma's
OL,15,Fdeath," she said.
OL,17,FMs Wood added that their behaviour in
OL,18,Fcourt had been "reprehensible" as they
OL,19,Fsought to blame medical professionals
OL,20,Ffor their daughter's death.
