OL,7,FMiss Shemirani's mother called her
OL,8,Ffriend who was nearby, before dialing
OL,9,F999 the day her daughter collapsed,
OL,10,Fthe inquest heard.
OL,12,FShe was later taken to the Royal
OL,13,FSussex County Hospital in Brighton
OL,14,Fwhere she died on July 24 of an
OL,15,F"unsurvivable brain injury" caused by
OL,16,Fher long cardiac arrest.
OL,18,FMiss Shemirani's brothers were not
OL,19,Ftold about their sister's collapse
OL,20,Funtil after her death.
